Interface RegisterableClientExecutableResolver

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ExecutableResolver

    public interface RegisterableClientExecutableResolver
extends ExecutableResolver
    Interface that a client executable resolver needs to implement in order for the cougar client to be registered with EV dynamically i.e. programmatically at runtime as opposed to via static spring config
